    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add 500ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[650ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [1L] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>with your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong>,<strong> Chinese rice wine </strong>and<strong> Dijon mustard</strong></p><p>Add a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and bring to the boil</p>",
