      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until cooked with a slight bite and the sausage meat is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Tip: Stir the orzo occasionally to stop it from sticking</p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach </strong>and pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
