        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked through, increase the heat to medium-high and add your <strong>double cream</strong> and <strong>spinach</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until the spinach has wilted and the sauce has thickened – this is your <strong>one pan creamy sausage, mushroom & spinach orzo</strong></p>",
